videos.description: Illinois' Ayo Dosunmu drains a quick 3-pointer for the Fighting Illini as it leads No. 9 Michigan State early.
videos.headline: Dosunmu drains 3 off good ball movement

videos.description: Illinois' Ayo Dosunmu makes two good defensive plays both leading to fast-break buckets at the other end.
videos.headline: Dosunmu steals and scores on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: Illinois' Giorgi Bezhanishvili grabs the lob and puts home the alley-oop late in the first half against Michigan State.
videos.headline: Bezhanishvili puts up big alley-oop

videos.description: Michigan State's Aaron Henry misses the open dunk, but the ball bounces out to Cassius Winston who drains the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Winston makes 3 off a missed dunk

videos.description: Xavier Tillman gets the big putback as No. 9 Michigan State comes back and leads Illinois by three points in the second half.
videos.headline: Tillman gets big putback for Spartans

videos.description: Illinois' Ayo Dosunmu hits consecutive 3-pointers to give Illinois a 6-point lead late in the second half.
videos.headline: Dosunmu drains clutch 3 pointer to extend lead

videos.description: Illinois fans storm the court after upsetting No. 9 Michigan State 79-74.
videos.headline: Fans storm court after upsetting Michigan State
